      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-06-23T05:06:35Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We referred to it as the \"upload server\" in the docs for |url| above and we should be consistent. However, it may just be better to say the attachments are captured with each report. This option doesn\u0027t necessarily imply upload and some Crashpad clients do use Crashpad for report capture, but not upload.",
